# 🧠 Front-End Development Quiz | Task 3 - ApexPlanet Internship

This is a simple yet interactive **Front-End Development Quiz** project built as part of **Task 3** of the **Web Development Internship** at **ApexPlanet Software Pvt Ltd**.

## 🚀 Project Objective

The goal of this project is to:
- Build an interactive quiz using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**
- Strengthen JavaScript skills by handling DOM events and logic
- Practice responsive design for multiple screen sizes

## 🛠️ Features

- Multiple-choice quiz on **Front-End Development**
- Real-time score calculation and feedback
- Responsive layout for mobile, tablet, and desktop
- Clean and modern UI

## 📚 Technologies Used

- HTML5  
- CSS3 (with Media Queries)  
- JavaScript (ES6)

